==發行==
[[二十世紀福斯|二十世紀福斯]]將電影排於2016年12月25日在美國上映，原本的上映日為2016年11月11日。而該檔期則改由2016年9月30日的《[[怪奇孤兒院_(電影)|怪奇孤兒院]]》頂替。

後來，又改至2016年12月23日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Ridley Scott’s ‘Alien: Covenant’ Moved Up to Summer 2017|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/alien-covenant-release-date-ridley-scott-1201717409/|accessdate=March 14, 2016|work=Variety|date=February 28, 2016|archive-date=2016-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412123507/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/alien-covenant-release-date-ridley-scott-1201717409/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hidden-figures-release-date-christmas-938618|title=It's Official: Fox's 'Hidden Figures' NASA Film to Get Oscar-Qualifying Limited Release|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|first=Hilary|last=Lewis|date=October 15, 2016|accessdate=October 15, 2016|archive-date=2019-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212105202/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hidden-figures-release-date-christmas-938618|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===評價===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於156條評論，新鮮度39%，平均評分5／10，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/why_him |title=Why Him? (2016) |publisher=Fandango Media |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=December 24, 2016 |archive-date=2019-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190523153419/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/why_him/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]獲得39分，整體評價不佳<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/why-him |title=Why Him? (2016) |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |website=Metacritic |accessdate=December 23, 2016 |archive-date=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711030444/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/why-him |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的評價在A+至F間落於「B+」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |accessdate=2020-10-10 |archive-date=2019-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210223808/https://m.cinemascore.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===票房===
《惱爸偏頭痛》估計能在首映週末從2800間戲院中，獲得1000萬至1400萬美元的票房收入<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/12/rogue-one-star-wars-passengers-jennifer-lawrence-sing-collateral-beauty-will-smith-christmas-box-office-1201869720/ |title=Will ‘Rogue One’ Vanquish The Christmas B.O. Competition? |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2016-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161216145243/http://deadline.com/2016/12/rogue-one-star-wars-passengers-jennifer-lawrence-sing-collateral-beauty-will-smith-christmas-box-office-1201869720/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=McClintock|first1=Pamela|title=Christmas Box-Office Crush: 'Sing,' 'Passengers,' 'Assassin's Creed' to Battle 'Rogue One'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-projections-sing-passengers-assassins-creed-battle-rogue-one-957607|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|accessdate=December 20, 2016|archive-date=2016-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223145428/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-projections-sing-passengers-assassins-creed-battle-rogue-one-957607|dead-url=no}}</ref>。首週末四天累計1670萬美元，位居當週第四<ref name="opening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/12/why-him-975k-thursday-previews-box-office-1201875344/|title=With ‘Fences,’ ‘La La Land’ Enter Top 10 As ‘Rogue One’ & ‘Sing’ Rule Holiday – Monday AM Update|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2016-12-27|archive-date=2018-06-23|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http://deadline.com/2016/12/why-him-975k-thursday-previews-box-office-1201875344/&date=2018-06-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

